{"tid":2266173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發！有源頭不明個案曾往銀礦灣渡假酒店Staycation 疑再傳染2人","createTime":"2020-11-01T05:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T10:03:23.000Z","uid":5195,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"03c188870d5b872ed1012ae8c76ccf36e5ad72e5","tid":2266173,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:51:25.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎疫情一直未能「清零」，昨日（31日）錄得3宗確診，全屬輸入。據悉，今日錄得約7宗確診，由於有源頭不明個案，衞生署下午4時半將召開記者會，意味本地零確診再斷纜。據了解，今日的源頭不明個案曾到銀礦灣渡假酒店Staycation，並最少有2宗關連個案，不排除他們曾一起去Staycation。<br />\n另外，消息指，昨日在大埔那打素醫院有一名26歲女子初步確診。她經急症室檢疫發現，懷疑是源頭不明本地個案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/ZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=fa62eb89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I%2F&h=392dfcb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/ZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I/</a>"},{"pid":"eaf0159bcdc1be8fcd7b404b95954d4b7304b007","tid":2266173,"uid":284432,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"369da9d810adba15f94eb17ba876987342b2f2e9","tid":2266173,"uid":155818,"like":18,"dislike":9,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"Staycation啊拿<br />\n爆多D爆勁D<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc6e191a6d5c84b91b34af1c678aa41bdf09e3c","tid":2266173,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"369da9d810adba15f94eb17ba876987342b2f2e9","tid":2266173,"uid":155818,"like":18,"dislike":9,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"Staycation啊拿<br />\n爆多D爆勁D<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:09:10.000Z","msg